<body>

<h1 class="drink-title">Boulevardier</h1>

<img class="drink-photo" src="../images/boulevardier.jpg" alt="boulevardier">

<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul class="ingredients">
    <li>3/2 oz bourbon or rye whiskey</li>
    <li>1 oz Campari</li>
    <li>1 oz sweet vermouth</li>
</ul>

<h2>Instructions</h2>
<ol class="instructions">
    <li>Add all ingredients to a mixing glass with ice.</li>
    <li>Stir until well chilled.</li>
    <li>Strain into a rocks glass over fresh ice.</li>
    <li>Garnish with an orange peel.</li>
</ol>

